comments: Very helpful professor. The classroom time was well oranized and with his help I got a good grade even I don\'t like Math very much.

If you don\'t mind being lost all the time take this class. The instructor really tried but what he taught and what was on the test was VERY different. Also gave us study material for final which ended up being entirely different. I feel like I wasted my time. If you don\'t have good grasp on the material you will spend hours at the tutor.!

Not my fav teacher, not sure if it was him or the course but we sped through the material and completed it 1 month of school still left in order to study for the final. Class avg 70, spent most of my time at the tutor relearning all sections, but he did try. Learned more at the tutor than in this class, take at a com college if you can.
I didn\'t really get him, but he is gorgeous so that\'s why I showed up to class. I don\'t think I actually learned anything though.
SUPER HOT!!! Hottest German professor ever! Take him, you\'ll love it!
